entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You recovered Sinis' missing medical equipment for him from the Deflarians.
entries.journal_entry_description: Sinis wants you to investigate the crash of a ship containing some medical equipment he was expecting.  He wants to know what became of this equipment in the hopes you can recover some of it for him.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Sinis gave you the coordinates to a location where the ship containing his medical equipment crashed.  Go to this location and see if you can find out anything for him.
entries.task01_comm_message_text: Why are Deflarian scavengers poking around the wreckage?  They are a well known criminal organization.  Perhaps they are involved somehow.  Eliminate a few of them and find out what it is they are searching for.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Sinis wants you to find out why Deflarian scavengers are hanging around and searching the crash site.  Kill these criminals until you find out what they are up to.
entries.task02_journal_entry_title: Kill Deflarian Scavengers for a Clue
entries.task03_comm_message_text: Now what would they want with the flight recorder? Take the recorder to a friend of mine named Yorick. He may be able to get the data off of it.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Take the flight recorder to Yorick.  Sinis thinks he may be able to recover the data from it.
entries.task05_comm_message_text: Yorick tells me the flight recorder was modified.  It may not even be from the right ship.  It is time for answers.  I am sending you the location of a communications post the Deflarians use.  Head over there and investigate.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Yorick says the damaged flight recorder was modified by someone.  Sinis wants you to kill Deflarian guards till you have 6 access cards.  After that you should be able to decipher the code and gain access to their private communications.
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Sinis wants you to find out more information about what the Deflarian organization is up to by accessing their communications terminal with the cards you got off the guards.
entries.task08_comm_message_text: I am sending you the location of the source of many communications to this terminal.  The communications hint of some equipment these pirates are trying to sell to an unknown buyer.
entries.task09_journal_entry_description: Sinis wants you to investigate the location he says is the origin of many communications between the Deflarians.
entries.task10_journal_entry_description: Sinis wants you to recover the missing medical equipment. For good measure, kill 8 Deflarian enforcers and the Deflarian lieutenant as well.
entries.task11_journal_entry_description: You have done well. I'm dispatching a ship to load the medical equipment you have secured.  Return to me and I shall reward you.
entries.task12_journal_entry_description: Sinis wants you to defeat the Deflarian lieutenant.
entries.task13_journal_entry_description: Sinis wants you to defeat 8 Deflarian enforcers.
entries.task14_journal_entry_description: The medical equipment!  Please recover it, you will have to eliminate some of these scum as well.
